---
title: Lemongrass and Coconut Chicken Thighs with Lime Basmati Rice
description: Thai cuisine is known for its love of aromatic ingredients. In that spirit, we've packed this recipe with lemongrass, curry paste and coconut milk, which will have your kitchen smelling heavenly. Add some fluffy rice and veggies on the side, and you’ve got a meal that’s both delicious and satisfying!
